<p>Examples of appropriate places for partisan political posters:</p>
<ul>
<li>Party Headquarters,</li>
<li>Campaign Rally.</li>
</ul>
<p>Example of inappropriate places for partisan political posters:</p>
<ul>
<li>The local produce stand.</li>
</ul>
<p>I'm not arguing against your first-amendment right to free speech.  And I don't want to infringe on that right at all, but you did just lose a customer, if only because I find your politics distasteful.</p>

